Movie Review

This is the Fkk Nudist Naturalist Czech Nudist Camp video made in 1994 but the location is in Yugoslavia. Length of movie is 50.31 minutes. The video is a small screen and therefore full screen its not so good. The overall video is a little weird to me but there is nothing really inappropriate in it. There is no sex, touching, or anything close to sexual. However, it is a nudist camp for families and therefore there are naked people there of all ages, from very young children to their parents. This might be alright on that camp but I am surprised why they would let anyone, or would want anyone to record this on tape even though it is supposed to be as a documentary supposedly.

Video: 6.5 out of 10 for small size screen
Sound: 9 out of 10

Verdict: Not sure why anyone would download this or want this so... maybe only out of curiosity like me.
